# My Project

A sample Java project created with Genesis using JSON structure.

## Usage

To create a project from this structure:

```bash
genesis new --name my-project --structure project-structure-example.json
```

Or use a JSON string directly:

```bash
genesis new --name my-project --structure '{"my-project": {"src": {"main.py": "print('Hello')"}, "README.md": "# Project"}}'
```
